    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Ready for the Road! Need a dependable car to get you from A to B without stretching your budget? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives well for daily use, though you'll notice some signs of wear and minor imperfections that come with a well-used car. Nothing here is a dealbreaker; it's simply an honest, practical vehicle at an honest price. If you're looking for solid transportation with room to add your own TLC, this could be a great fit! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself. \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Rare opportunity to own a truly mint-condition vehicle that stands out from the crowd! This car presents beautifully inside and out \u2014 the exterior gleams with no visible blemishes, the interior is spotless and fresh, and everything works exactly as it should. Mechanically, it's in outstanding shape, running smoothly and confidently with no known issues whatsoever. Whether you're a discerning buyer looking for the best or simply want a car you can enjoy worry-free from day one, this one delivers. Don't miss your chance to drive home something genuinely special!",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Exceptional Mint-Condition Beauty \u2013 The Real Deal! \ud83d\ude97\n\nThis is the used car you've been dreaming about! In true mint condition, this vehicle has been lovingly maintained and shows virtually no signs of wear \u2014 inside or out. The interior is spotless, the exterior gleams, and everything runs exactly as it should. This isn't 'good for its age' \u2014 it's genuinely outstanding by any standard. If you want a used car that delivers a near-new experience without the new-car price tag, this is your opportunity. Come see it in person and you'll understand why mint condition really means something here!",
      "price": 50000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make a decision. The exterior shows clear signs of regular use \u2014 expect visible scratches, some paint fading, and minor dents consistent with a car that has seen daily driving. The interior is functional but worn, with noticeable scuffing on the seats and trim, and some wear on high-contact surfaces like the steering wheel and door handles. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term. This is a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who doesn't mind cosmetic imperfections and is comfortable with a vehicle that may require some attention. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged so you can make a fully informed decision.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, and buyers should enter with clear, realistic expectations. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and faded or chipped paint are visible on various panels. The body has not been repaired or touched up, and the cosmetic issues are immediately apparent. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and a general sense of prolonged use without significant maintenance. Mechanically, the vehicle runs but has known issues that will likely require attention; prospective buyers should budget for repairs. This car is best suited for someone seeking a project vehicle, a parts donor, or a very budget-conscious buyer who is comfortable with the risks and costs associated with a high-mileage, well-used automobile. No warranties or guarantees are implied. What you see is what you get, and we encourage an independent inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent so you know exactly what you're getting. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect noticeable dents, scratches, and paint fading throughout. The interior is similarly worn, with tears or heavy staining on the upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration from years of use. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to bring it to reliable daily-driver status \u2014 this is not a turn-key vehicle. It starts and moves under its own power, but a pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged so you understand the full scope of work needed. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, a hobbyist looking for a project, or someone who needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. Priced accordingly to reflect its current state honestly.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    }
